        public boolean terminateRental(java.lang.String drivingLicence)
        This method terminates the rental contract associated with the given driving licence. In effect, the driver is returning the car. The car is then available for rent by someone else. The method removes the record of the rental from the company's records (disassociating the car from the licence) and returns the amount of fuel in Litres required to fill the car's tank.
